<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a49c549-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s5109"><num value="5109">§ 5109.</num><heading> Relation of existing program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Proposals received by the Department of Energy before <date date="1988-11-17">November 17, 1988</date>, may be carried out without regard to changes in the management plan and research plan required by this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a49c54a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/680/s10">Pub. L. 100–680, § 10</ref>, <date date="1988-11-17">Nov. 17, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/4076">102 Stat. 4076</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
